name: dump

abort.description: abort execution of page after execution of dump tag

type.description: type of the dump (alias for format)

label.description: string; header for the dump output.

var.description: Variable to display. Enclose a variable name in pound signs

description:
Outputs variables for debugging purposes. Using cfdump, you can display the contents of simple variables, queries, 
  arrays, structures, and WDDX variables created with cfwddx. if no var attribute defined it dump the hole site information
